Package: xbomber
Version: 2.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, python, curl
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/Anon4You/XBomber
Description: A High-Performance SMS Bombing Tool for Educational Testing
   XBomber is a lightweight Python script designed to test the resilience of SMS gateways by sending a high volume of messages.
   It is optimized for the Termux environment on Android, providing a portable solution for security researchers and penetration testers.


